videos.description: Alex Barnes runs it in for the first touchdown of the season for Kansas State.
videos.headline: Barnes punches in first touchdown of the season for Wildcats

videos.description: Jayd Kirby  comes off the edge and sacks Hayden Hildebrand for the first sack of his career
videos.headline: Jayd Kirby records first career sack.

videos.description: Brendon Cox ties the game at 10 in the 1st quarter
videos.headline: Cox ties game with 37-yard touchdown run.

videos.description: Jesse Ertz delivers a touchdown pass to Isaiah Zuber to retake the lead early in the 2nd quarter for the Wildcats
videos.headline: Ertz hits Zuber in corner of endzone for touchdown.

videos.description: Hayden Hildebrand throws touchdown to  Roman Gordon in the 2nd quarter.
videos.headline: Hildebrand tosses touchdown to Gordon.

videos.description: Byron Pringle uses impressive juke move on defender on his way to a 55-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Byron Pringle jukes defender en route to a touchdown.

videos.description: D.J. Reed gets his second big return of the game for the Wildcats, this time for a touchdown
videos.headline: D.J. Reed returns punt 62-yards for a touchdown.

videos.description: D.J. Reed adds an Interception to his impressive game.
videos.headline: Reed continues big game with Interception.

videos.description: Dalton Schoen adds to Wildcats lead with touchdown in the final minute of the 2nd quarter.
videos.headline: Schoen catches and runs for 70-yard touchdown.

videos.description: The Wildcats' lead is extended to 29 with a 69-yard touchdown pass from Ertz to Harris.
videos.headline: Harris goes for a 69-yard touchdown.

videos.description: Elijah Sullivan forces fumble, which is then recovered by Denzel Goolsby.
videos.headline: Wildcats force, then recover, a fumble.

videos.description: Dalvin Warmack scores his first touchdown as a Wildcat with 18-yard run.
videos.headline: Warmack runs 18-yards for a touchdown.
